{"tid":288624,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"原 來 係 特 登 嘅！吳 業 坤 知 道 打 錯 字 唔 改","createTime":"2017-06-18T10:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T12:58:42.000Z","uid":35964,"like":5,"dislike":218,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64ad8f0671874d1cc2580ac2d3d2a43c44d46432","tid":288624,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:30:35.000Z","msg":"歌手吳業坤及王灝兒（JW）到電視城演出《明愛暖萬心》，提到吳業坤在網上再爆新錯體詞語「好想釣人食飯」，JW也笑言：「我都有留言問佢想點呀？但係都幾搞笑，幾有創意！」<br />\n<br />\n吳業坤自「食好西」後，每隔一段時間就爆出獨特的「潮語」，他說：「我覺得有時可以同啲同事、Fans互動吓，係幾開心！唔使咁認真嘅，可能有啲人覺得，你咁講係想做啲乜嘢呀？其實想同大家放鬆吓，傾吓計。（真係咁啱打錯？）除咗『食好西』係唔小心嘅！有啲係睇到打錯咗但冇改，我覺得一笑置之，大家開心！釣字同約字係因為我輸入法打速成，㩒錯隔籬，不過一睇就明，除非心邪！我會努力，或者JW遲啲教我中文啦！」<br />\n<br />\n聽日生日<br />\n<br />\n將於明日（6月18日）過26歲生日的JW，已經開了生日P，她說：「因為要做嘢同埋父親節，所以提早咗。（男友慶生好Sweet？）我哋成班朋友嘅，今年都冇乜收到啲咩禮物，因為都冇同佢哋講我想要啲咩！（講就有禮物？）都唔係㗎，最緊要係見到啲朋友，因為依家愈大愈忙。（有咩生日願望？）開開心心，身體健康，可以喺紅館開演唱會！等我問前輩（吳業坤）取經先！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170617/photo/bkn-20170617225212094-0617_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170618000618\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170617%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170617225212094-0617_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170618000618&h=7b660b2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d26427631a76066e6c90d384d075b3aa743d1ba9","tid":288624,"uid":89660,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:31:50.000Z","msg":"又po c坤上黎做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無人想知"},{"pid":"c746bf9f41fc1777d816c16287ed0677a7b76fbf","tid":288624,"uid":82917,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:18:52.000Z","msg":"呢條柒頭好煩"},{"pid":"353d7fa19408abe9f113d4a0053446ce51a3002c","tid":288624,"uid":24634,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:22:10.000Z","msg":"原來食好西係出自呢條友<br />\n我仲諗邊條on9作d咁既野出黎<br />\n成街係度食好西食好西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e69c6e8b654e067ae444c06af5259dd173292df","tid":288624,"uid":89507,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:18:03.000Z","msg":"Stop Making Stupid People Famous"},{"pid":"ff3b77ebc2b283a999510b9f9a55f028cc006bd0","tid":288624,"uid":29929,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來食好西係出自呢條友<br />\n我仲諗邊條on9作d咁既野出黎<br />\n成街係度食好西食好西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢其實都幾聰明<br />\n發明呢個字<br />\n而家大家都有得用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de48a09909c65e72401b53a2fe9a4caf63ee827","tid":288624,"uid":56549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係好煩"},{"pid":"460db380ebd2ec82b4b65c177c77ca7bd408b9c7","tid":288624,"uid":65187,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"好想釣人食好西"},{"pid":"937588eb520ef3b52cd990b698700170e6becb02","tid":288624,"uid":123440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"唔係啊 真心問&hellip;<br />\n關我咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9781188dc12d8c4b43de368f952738341ef50af","tid":288624,"uid":42636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:24:05.000Z","msg":"偽毒樣衰搏出位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec530b89ba75a5a3e95152b43084837146675ad5","tid":288624,"uid":43308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:26:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f58040b22be49afe950488c1257cc62137e66c9f","tid":288624,"uid":12367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"釣字同約字係因為我輸入法打速成，㩒錯隔籬，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n